msgid "# Netloader Guide"
msgstr "# Netloader 指南"

msgid ""
"This guide provides instructions for using **Netloader** as a weight-loader "
"plugin for acceleration in **vLLM Ascend**."
msgstr "本指南介绍如何在 **vLLM Ascend** 中使用 **Netloader** 作为权重加载插件以加速。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使用方法"

msgid ""
"To enable Netloader, pass `--load-format=netloader` and provide "
"configuration via `--model-loader-extra-config` (as a JSON string). Below "
"are the supported configuration fields:"
msgstr ""
"要启用 Netloader，请传递 `--load-format=netloader` 并通过 `--model-loader-extra-"
"config`（以 JSON 字符串形式）提供配置。以下是支持的配置字段："

msgid "## Example Commands & Placeholders"
msgstr "## 示例命令与占位符"

msgid "> Replace parts in `` `<...>` `` before running."
msgstr "> 运行前请替换 `` `<...>` `` 中的内容。"

msgid "### Server"
msgstr "### 服务器端"

msgid "### Client"
msgstr "### 客户端"

msgid "#### Placeholder Descriptions"
msgstr "#### 占位符说明"

msgid ""
"- `<model_file>`: Path to the model file  \n"
"- `<model_name>`: Model name (must match between server & client)  \n"
"- `<port>`: Base listening port on server  \n"
"- `<server_IP>` + `<server_Port>`: IP and port of the Netloader server (from server log)  \n"
"- `<device_id_diff_from_server>`: Client device ID (must differ from server’s)  \n"
"- `<client_port>`: Port on which client listens"
msgstr ""
"- `<model_file>`：模型文件路径  \n"
"- `<model_name>`：模型名称（服务器和客户端必须一致）  \n"
"- `<port>`：服务器上的基础监听端口  \n"
"- `<server_IP>` + `<server_Port>`：Netloader 服务器的 IP 和端口（来自服务器日志）  \n"
"- `<device_id_diff_from_server>`：客户端设备 ID（必须与服务器不同）  \n"
"- `<client_port>`：客户端监听的端口"

msgid ""
"After startup, you can test consistency by issuing inference requests with "
"temperature = 0 and comparing outputs."
msgstr "启动后，您可以通过发送 temperature = 0 的推理请求并比较输出来测试一致性。"

msgid "## Note & Caveats"
msgstr "## 注意事项"

msgid ""
"- If Netloader is used, **each worker process** must bind a listening port. That port may be user-specified or assigned randomly. If user-specified, ensure it is available.  \n"
"- Netloader requires extra on-chip memory to establish HCCL connections (i.e. `HCCL_BUFFERSIZE`, default ~200 MB). Users should reserve sufficient capacity (e.g. via `--gpu-memory-utilization`).  \n"
"- It is recommended to set `VLLM_SLEEP_WHEN_IDLE=1` to mitigate unstable or slow connections/transmissions. Related info: [vLLM Issue #16660](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/16660), [vLLM PR #16226](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/16226)."
msgstr ""
"- 如果使用 Netloader，**每个工作进程**必须绑定一个监听端口。该端口可由用户指定或随机分配。如果由用户指定，请确保其可用。  \n"
"- Netloader 需要额外的片上内存来建立 HCCL 连接（即 `HCCL_BUFFERSIZE`，默认约 200 MB）。用户应预留足够的容量（例如通过 `--gpu-memory-utilization`）。  \n"
"- 建议设置 `VLLM_SLEEP_WHEN_IDLE=1` 以缓解连接/传输不稳定或缓慢的问题。相关信息：[vLLM Issue #16660](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/16660)，[vLLM PR #16226](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/16226)。"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"Netloader leverages high-bandwidth peer-to-peer (P2P) transfers between NPU "
"cards to load model weights. It is implemented as a plugin (via the "
"`register_model_loader` API added in vLLM 0.10). The workflow is:"
msgstr ""
"Netloader 利用 NPU 卡之间的高带宽点对点（P2P）传输来加载模型权重。它通过 vLLM 0.10 版本新增的 "
"`register_model_loader` API 以插件形式实现。其工作流程如下："

msgid ""
"1. A **server** preloads a model.  \n"
"2. A new **client** instance requests weight transfer.  \n"
"3. After validating that the model and partitioning match, the client uses HCCL collective communication (send/recv) to receive weights in the same order as stored in the model."
msgstr ""
"1. **服务端**预加载模型。  \n"
"2. 新的**客户端**实例请求权重传输。  \n"
"3. 在验证模型和分区匹配后，客户端使用 HCCL 集合通信（发送/接收）按照模型中存储的相同顺序接收权重。"

msgid ""
"The server runs alongside normal inference tasks via sub-threads and via "
"`stateless_init_torch_distributed_process_group` in vLLM. The client thus "
"takes over weight initialization without needing to load from storage."
msgstr ""
"服务端通过子线程以及 vLLM 中的 `stateless_init_torch_distributed_process_group` "
"与正常推理任务并行运行。因此，客户端无需从存储加载即可接管权重初始化。"

msgid "### Flowchart"
msgstr "### 流程图"

msgid "### Timing Diagram"
msgstr "### 时序图"

msgid "### Application Scenarios"
msgstr "### 应用场景"

msgid ""
"- **Reduce startup latency**: By reusing already loaded weights and transferring them directly between NPU cards, Netloader cuts down model loading time versus conventional remote/local pull strategies.  \n"
"- **Relieve network & storage load**: Avoid repeated downloads of weight files from remote repositories, thus reducing pressure on central storage and network traffic.  \n"
"- **Improve resource utilization & lower cost**: Faster loading allows less reliance on standby compute nodes; resources can be scaled up/down more flexibly.  \n"
"- **Enhance business continuity & high availability**: In failure recovery, new instances can quickly take over without long downtime, improving system reliability and user experience."
msgstr ""
"- **降低启动延迟**：通过复用已加载的权重并在 NPU 卡之间直接传输，Netloader 相比传统的远程/本地拉取策略，减少了模型加载时间。  \n"
"- **减轻网络与存储负载**：避免从远程仓库重复下载权重文件，从而减轻中央存储和网络流量的压力。  \n"
"- **提高资源利用率并降低成本**：更快的加载速度减少了对备用计算节点的依赖；资源可以更灵活地弹性伸缩。  \n"
"- **增强业务连续性与高可用性**：在故障恢复时，新实例无需长时间停机即可快速接管，提高了系统可靠性和用户体验。"

msgid ""
"| Field Name         | Type    | Description"
"                                                                                          "
"| Allowed Values / Notes"
"                                                                                       "
"|"
msgstr ""
"| 字段名称           | 类型    | 描述"
"                                                                                                "
"| 允许值 / 说明"
"                                                                                               "
"|"

msgid ""
"| **SOURCE**         | List    | Weight data sources. Each item is a map "
"with `device_id` and `sources`, specifying the rank and its endpoints "
"(IP:port). <br>Example: `{\"SOURCE\": [{\"device_id\": 0, \"sources\": "
"[\"10.170.22.152:19374\"]}, {\"device_id\": 1, \"sources\": "
"[\"10.170.22.152:11228\"]}]}` <br>If omitted or empty, fallback to default "
"loader. The SOURCE here is second priority. | A list of objects with keys "
"`device_id: int` and `sources: List[str]` |"
msgstr ""
"| **SOURCE**         | List    | 权重数据源。每个元素是一个包含 `device_id` 和 `sources` "
"的映射，指定 rank 及其端点（IP:端口）。<br>示例：`{\"SOURCE\": [{\"device_id\": 0, "
"\"sources\": [\"10.170.22.152:19374\"]}, {\"device_id\": 1, \"sources\": "
"[\"10.170.22.152:11228\"]}]}` <br>如果省略或为空，则回退到默认加载器。此处的 SOURCE 为第二优先级。 | "
"一个对象列表，键为 `device_id: int` 和 `sources: List[str]` |"

msgid ""
"| **MODEL**           | String  | The model name, used to verify consistency"
" between client and server.                                | Defaults to the"
" `--model` argument if not specified."
"                                                         |"
msgstr ""
"| **MODEL**           | String  | 模型名称，用于验证客户端与服务器之间的一致性。"
"                                | 如果未指定，默认为 `--model` 参数。"
"                                                         |"

msgid ""
"| **LISTEN_PORT**     | Integer | Base port for the server listener."
"                                                                   | The "
"actual port = `LISTEN_PORT + RANK`. If omitted, a random valid port is "
"chosen. Valid range: 1024–65535. If out of range, that server instance won’t"
" open a listener. |"
msgstr ""
"| **LISTEN_PORT**     | Integer | 服务器监听器的基端口。"
"                                                                   | 实际端口 = "
"`LISTEN_PORT + RANK`。如果省略，则选择一个随机有效端口。有效范围：1024–65535。如果超出范围，该服务器实例将不会打开监听器。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| **INT8_CACHE**      | String  | Behavior for handling int8 parameters in "
"quantized models.                                           | One of "
"`[\"hbm\", \"dram\", \"no\"]`. <br> - `hbm`: copy original int8 parameters "
"to high-bandwidth memory (HBM) (may cost a lot of HBM). <br> - `dram`: copy "
"to DRAM. <br> - `no`: no special handling (may lead to divergence or "
"unpredictable behavior). Default: `\"no\"`. |"
msgstr ""
"| **INT8_CACHE**      | String  | 处理量化模型中 int8 参数的行为。"
"                                           | 可选值：`[\"hbm\", \"dram\", "
"\"no\"]`。<br> - `hbm`：将原始 int8 参数复制到高带宽内存（HBM）（可能消耗大量 HBM）。<br> - `dram`：复制到"
" DRAM。<br> - `no`：不做特殊处理（可能导致发散或不可预测的行为）。默认值：`\"no\"`。 |"

msgid ""
"| **INT8_CACHE_NAME** | List    | Names of parameters to which `INT8_CACHE` "
"is applied (i.e. filtering).                               | Default: `None`"
" (means no filtering—all parameters)."
"                                                         |"
msgstr ""
"| **INT8_CACHE_NAME** | List    | 应用 `INT8_CACHE` 的参数名称（即过滤条件）。"
"                               | 默认值：`None`（表示不过滤——所有参数）。"
"                                                         |"

msgid ""
"| **OUTPUT_PREFIX**   | String  | Prefix for writing per-rank listener "
"address/port files in server mode.                              | If set, "
"each rank writes to `{OUTPUT_PREFIX}{RANK}.txt` (text), content = `IP:Port`."
"                         |"
msgstr ""
"| **OUTPUT_PREFIX**   | String  | 在服务器模式下，写入每个 rank 的监听器地址/端口文件的前缀。"
"                              | 如果设置，每个 rank 将写入 "
"`{OUTPUT_PREFIX}{RANK}.txt`（文本），内容为 `IP:Port`。                         |"

msgid ""
"| **CONFIG_FILE**     | String  | Path to a JSON file specifying the above "
"configuration.                                              | If provided, "
"the SOURCE inside this file has **first priority** (overrides SOURCE in "
"other configs).          |"
msgstr ""
"| **CONFIG_FILE**     | String  | 指定上述配置的 JSON 文件路径。"
"                                              | 如果提供，此文件中的 SOURCE "
"具有**第一优先级**（覆盖其他配置中的 SOURCE）。          |"
